{
  "bookId": "laozi-boshu",
  "num": 71,
  "title": "第七十一章（知病）",
  "author": "老子",
  "authorId": "Laozi",
  "dynasty": "周",
  "era": "周",
  "genre": "prose",
  "verses": [
    {
      "text": "知不知，尚矣。"
    },
    {
      "text": "不知不知，病矣。"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以聖人之不病。"
    },
    {
      "text": "以亓病病也，"
    },
    {
      "text": "是以不病。"
    }
  ],
  "sections": {},
  "annotations": [],
  "layers": {
    "heshanggong": [
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 8,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不知道言知，是乃德之病。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 8,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "夫唯能病苦眾人有強知之病，是以不自病也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-3",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 8,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "聖人無此強知之病者，以其常苦眾人有此病。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "heshanggong-4",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 16,
          "end": 17
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "以比非人，故不自病。夫聖人懷通達之知，託於不知者，欲使天下質樸忠正，各守純性。小人不知道意，而妄行強知之事以自顯著，內傷精神，減壽消年也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ],
    "wangbi": [
      {
        "id": "wangbi-1",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 8,
          "end": 8
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "不知知之不足任則病也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 4,
          "start": 5,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
